Ever since translocate was introduced, I hate going any where without a wizard in a group.  <br>
<br>
On the expo grind side, a wizard can send a party member home if they are leaving early.  A well played wizard can make a great difference when pulls go bad.<br>
<br>
A wizard with their epic is a great party member, and in raid situations, nothing beats a battery of high level wizards to finish off who ever your fighting.<br>
